---
title: Bacon, Apple, Chicken and Cheddar Melts with Honey-Mustard Dipper
description: Here's a sandwich that's sure to be a hit with the whole family! Sweet apples help to cut the richness from the bacon and cheese, while a side of BBQ-spiced potatoes get honey-mustard mayo as a dunking buddy.
